This is how to solve of s:
  Remember that result is []
  Remember that i is diff of s's length and 1
  Do this s's length times:
    Remember that x is item i in s
    When x is at least 97, then:
      When x is at most 122, then:
        Add result to diff of x and 32
      But, if not:
        Add result to x
      End when
    But, if not:
      When x is at least 65, then:
        When x is at most 90, then:
          Add result to sum of x and 32
        But, if not:
          Add result to x
        End when
      But, if not:
        Add result to x
      End when
    End when
    Decrease i by 1
  End do
  The answer is result
